  "description": "A comprehensive architectural operating system designed for the People's Republic of Bangladesh. NUPA-BD adapts to the centralized administrative structure by leveraging the NBR's existing tax apparatus, utilizing a 40/40/20 Sovereign Adaptive Waterfall to align federal, divisional, and hub-level incentives.",
